    CacheImplCommon
    Base class for cache classes.
    ConfiguredCacheImpl
    A cache that is configured from a file.
    DefaultCacheImpl
    A cache that uses the default xml file (etc/default.xml).
    ECASTAlgorithm
    Cache eviction algorithm that writes evicted records to the server.
    ECASTAlgorithmConfig
    Configuration data for the eviction algorithm.
    NullCacheImpl
    Null Cache that sends everything straight to the server.
